  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nIn altair, processing attestation and sync aggregate takes so much time due to the update to BeaconState tree frequently\r\n<img width=\"1169\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2021-07-22 at 17 11 42\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/126623691-96d793c7-2cb6-497b-8929-d256703bc3f2.png\">\r\n\r\n+ For attestation, we update the participation status of every attesters to the tree\r\n+ For sync aggregation, we update the balance of all sync committee participants\r\n\r\nSometimes the time to process a block is even bigger than an epoch, I imagine it'd be not a small issue when we upgrade prater to altair.\r\n[0721_sync_altair_devnet_1.cpuprofile.zip](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/files/6861548/0721_sync_altair_devnet_1.cpuprofile.zip)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\n+ No solution right now, need to write performance test for processing a block first.",
